?<br />\n香港d死黑警，做嘢啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀sorry,我錯，我忘記咗添，警黑合作嘛，你地係teammate黎喎。唔拉得!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221e1ff07d6d51ff7b5242e435cdacf2dc551766","tid":1476453,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:39:12.000Z","msg":"理撚得你 無證就無證啦"},{"pid":"358deab432ee570f922a680435f454e159708fba","tid":1476453,"uid":151143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"傳開去<br />\n<br />\n呢條大陸仔違反逗留條件，係可拘捕罪行，市民行使公民拘捕權，用咗索帶做法唔理想，但可接受"},{"pid":"2b45665557745e6224de2d0b2feb70bfe201e704","tid":1476453,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8192007fefb4dcf9e546b2ada6ac7fef4d3ad31","tid":1476453,"uid":66991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ec6f4e9b5c91fb29c81b1cdb608c6fafd4822d","tid":1476453,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:52:33.000Z","msg":"就算係，你係國際社會面前行私刑<br />\n都係說不過去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:37:07.000Z","msg":"你講緊啲狗定黑社會"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:40:28.000Z","msg":"黑社會同黑警當然係<br />\n但機場打記者，更似係純粹嘅情緒發泄<br />\n當然我知香港人呢兩個月被壓過咗好耐<br />\n但絕對唔係明智之舉"},{"pid":"d